
#############

* zram + zswap

   zramctl /dev/zram0 -s 1G
   mkswap /dev/zram0
   swapon /dev/zram0
   zramctl ; cat /proc/swaps ; free -h

   zramctl /dev/zram0 -s 1G
   mkfs.ext4 /dev/zram0
   mount /dev/zram0 /tmp

   zramctl /dev/zram1 -s 1G
   mkfs.ext4 /dev/zram1
   mount /dev/zram1 /dev/shm

-------------

 cryptographic api - > compression - > lzo

  CONFIG_CRYPTO_LZO

 device drivers - > block devices - > compressed ram block device support

  CONFIG_ZRAM

 memory management options - > support for paging of anonymous memory

  CONFIG_SWAP

-------------

